有咩唔同?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T11:12:45.000Z","msg":"Framework 係 base on 個 language去改良（本質都係果套language)<br />\n<br />\n好似front end咁<br />\nAngular React Vue都係base on JavaScript去改良<br />\n<br />\n舉個例，你直接學react，學嘅時候未必會明ES6嘅野，或者0基礎直學睇Doc學未必睇得未<br />\n<br />\n而當你學完react想學埋Angular雙修，但某啲地方唔同，你冇JS底又變到好似由頭學過咁<br />\n<br />\n個人認為打好底再學會好啲"},{"pid":"2d2ba78cd326f08438301584a139c592c86a0119","tid":1040732,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bba2f4fe2d937e9fd4a48b18ba705fbb47129689","tid":1040732,"uid":144182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f0282ed1bfe969535059ed6e992da7809660b58","tid":1040732,"uid":137335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:48:07.000Z","msg":"你本身識JS係識到咩程度先，唔識basic直接學framework我驚你會唔明"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T11:00:56.000Z","msg":"應該還可以, FRAMWORK 都普通有咩唔同?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T11:31:35.000Z","msg":"好多時網上 tutorial 學完，結果唔係 best practices，又要重新學過<br />\n<br />\n因為個 React 同 Angular 早過 ES6 出<br />\n為左方便 programmer, 加左啲額外功能, 例如mixins, decorations, class<br />\nES6 出左之後，上面講果啲野個定義唔同左，成套功能變左obsoleted，而網上 tutorial 繼續教緊舊果套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1984bc2b05e9b32dc270942a8f8cf22a067f978a","tid":1040732,"uid":14476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d2ba78cd326f08438301584a139c592c86a0119","tid":1040732,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bba2f4fe2d937e9fd4a48b18ba705fbb47129689","tid":1040732,"uid":144182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f0282ed1bfe969535059ed6e992da7809660b58","tid":1040732,"uid":137335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:48:07.000Z","msg":"你本身識JS係識到咩程度先，唔識basic直接學framework我驚你會唔明"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T11:00:56.000Z","msg":"應該還可以, FRAMWORK 都普通有咩唔同?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T11:31:35.000Z","msg":"好多時網上 tutorial 學完，結果唔係 best practices，又要重新學過<br />\n<br />\n因為個 React 同 Angular 早過 ES6 出<br /